title: Episode 19: Rocket Moon
itunes:title: Episode 19: Rocket Moon
description:
Bobby is eager to see a leprechaun die.

Someone has a giant throbbing varicosed beef thermometer.

Always put your money on American heart.

We talk about sibling love, the Kims of Comedy, and the varying effects of video games on the human brain.

Oh and fight picks for the big UFC weekend!

 

Recorded December 7, 2015

Music by Bobby Lee

Instagram: @tigerbelly

Twitter: @thetigerbelly

www.thetigerbelly.com
